$$\boldsymbol\Sigma = \frac{1}{N}\sum_{n=1}^N(\textbf x_n - \bar{\textbf x})(\textbf x_n - \bar{\textbf x})^T$$
or
$$\boldsymbol\Sigma = \frac{1}{N}(\textbf X - \bar{\textbf X})(\textbf X - \bar{\textbf X})^T$$

